OL,7,FITV News' Arts Editor Nina Nannar
OL,8,Fspoke to Oscar-nominated costume
OL,9,Fdesigner Holly Waddington and Chicken
OL,10,FShop date star Amelia Dimoldenberg
OL,12,FLast year, the red carpet was
OL,13,Fchampagne coloured, but that change
OL,14,Fdidn't last for long.
OL,16,FIt's red again this year, and scores
OL,17,Fof cameras were in evidence to record
OL,18,Fit being unrolled in place by the
OL,19,FDolby Theatre on Hollywood Boulevard.
