OL,7,FAnother tradition likely to be
OL,8,Fmaintained is the success of behind
OL,9,Fthe camera.
OL,11,FThere are nominations for the costume
OL,12,Fand set designers for Barbie, filmed
OL,13,Fmainly in Leavesden studios in
OL,14,FHertfordshire.
OL,16,FA nomination, too, for the costume
OL,17,Fdesigner on Poor Things, Holly
OL,18,FWaddington, who recently triumphed in
OL,19,Fthat category at the BAFTAs.
