OL,3,CLondon's cost crisis will hinder
OL,4,Ctalent, says Poor Things costume
OL,5,Cdesigner
OL,7,FShe told me that the pipeline of
OL,8,Ftalent coming into her sector is under
OL,9,Fthreat because of the astronomical
OL,10,Fcosts involved in living in London.
OL,12,FShe says she learned her craft in the
OL,13,Fcostumes shops and west end theatre of
OL,14,Fthe capital, but young people wishing
OL,15,Fto follow a career trajectory like
OL,16,Fhers will likely struggle to afford to
OL,17,Flive there on what are often low wages
OL,18,Fat the start of their career in the
OL,19,Findustry.
