OL,7,FJohnnie Burn who is nominated for best
OL,8,Fsound for his work on The Zone Of
OL,9,FInterest, says the UK produces
OL,10,Fcreative and experimental talent in
OL,11,Ftechnical skills in the industry.
OL,13,FHe was tasked with depicting the
OL,14,Fhorrors of The Holocaust through
OL,15,Fsound, which he spent more than a year
OL,16,Fresearching. The result is
OL,17,Fextraordinary and chilling.
