OL,7,FFor all the high profile success of
OL,8,FBritish cast and crew, it has been a
OL,9,Fdifficult time for many in an industry
OL,10,Fhit by the recent strikes by Hollywood
OL,11,Factors and writers, coupled with the
OL,12,Fafter effects of the pandemic.
OL,14,FFilm and TV are struggling with a
OL,15,Fskills shortage, at a time when
OL,16,Fproduction is booming in the UK due in
OL,17,Fpart to streaming giants' huge spend
OL,18,Fon content for their platforms.
