OL,4,Ctalent, says Poor Things costume
OL,5,Cdesigner
OL,7,FSo the news this week of tax breaks
OL,8,Ffor England's film and TV studios, and
OL,9,Ffor independent British films, is
OL,10,Fwelcomed, described by some as game-
OL,11,Fchanging for home-grown productions.
OL,13,FThere's good news too for some more
OL,14,Fhome-grown talent.
OL,16,FAmelia Dimoldenberg began a column in
OL,17,Fher local youth club magazine, then
OL,18,Fmade it into a YouTube series called
OL,19,FChicken Shop Date in which she
OL,20,Finterviewed stars, first from music
OL,21,Fwith people like Ghetts and AJ Tracey.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/9
