OL,3,CLondon's cost crisis will hinder
OL,4,Ctalent, says Poor Things costume
OL,5,Cdesigner
OL,7,FSince her series became a huge
OL,8,Fsuccess, she has been attracting the
OL,9,Flikes of Jennifer Lawrence to sit in
OL,10,Fher local chicken shop in Edgware to
OL,11,Fchat to her.
OL,13,FNow, Dimoldenberg has been give the
OL,14,Fjob of red carpet interviewer by the
OL,15,FOscars academy as well as social media
OL,16,Fambassador, in short making her the
OL,17,Fface of the Oscars online.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
