OL,5,Cdesigner
OL,7,FIt is no doubt hoped she can use her
OL,8,Fhuge social media following to bring a
OL,9,Fyounger audience to watch the Oscars
OL,10,Fcoverage.
OL,12,FIt is a smart move by the academy,
OL,13,Fwhich has also brought in strict rules
OL,14,Fof diversity and inclusion for
OL,15,Fcompeting films.
OL,17,FIt should all make for a good night on
OL,18,FSunday, allowing those behind the
OL,19,Fcamera to step out to the front and be
OL,20,Frightly honoured for their work.
